<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1915-08-23T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1915-08-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="608" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d608">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.51/413.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Davis</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Port au Prince</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-23">
                                    <hi rend="italic">August 23, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Referring to your August 12. Dutch boat arrived yesterday. No gourdes
                            aboard. Representative of Banknote Company has just been in to show me a
                            cable from New York saying that no more shipping until advised by
                            him.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Davis.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>